{"type": "article", "id": 26750, "title": "扩音器", "description": "", "date": "2016-05-13T06:34:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 400262, "comment_count": 2, "praise_count": 43, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702145801eAQG734rgnNIsZVP.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://shufflethree.com/\" target=\"_blank\">Shuffle Three</a> 最近推出了这款名为 Audiovase 的扩音器，让你不需要蓝牙音响也可以畅快地听音乐了。相比蓝牙配对、插入连接线之类繁琐的步骤，它使用起来非常方便，只要放入手机即可。扩音器可以装下目前各类主流的手机，哪怕它外面装了保护壳也是绰绰有余，底部还留有一个空隙容纳手机充电线，保证了续航。目前这款产品正在 <a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/726246208/the-audiovasetm-by-shuffle-threetm\">Kickstarter</a> 上进行众筹，早鸟价为 20 美元，唯一美中不足的是它不能寄往美国以外的地区。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145759U6VlRi0XEsOYoeDK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145759KvwVRbDQxiCptIyn.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702145759sN8fBdxV2LQM1aYv.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66285714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021458003gpak7xq50c9EioD.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.48190476\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n"}